210
00:14:37,375 --> 00:14:38,333
Agarrem-nos!

211
00:14:38,416 --> 00:14:40,958
Vá, apanha as tartarugas. Vá.

212
00:14:41,791 --> 00:14:44,041
- De que bairro és?
- Do Quinze.

213
00:14:44,833 --> 00:14:46,250
- Daqui?
- Sim.

214
00:14:48,541 --> 00:14:50,208
São os meus colegas.

215
00:14:52,041 --> 00:14:55,041
- Têm tartarugas?
- Pronto. Tenho de ir. Adeus.

216
00:14:55,583 --> 00:14:58,958
Momo? Quanto te devo? Põe o dela na conta.

217
00:15:00,541 --> 00:15:01,416
Belo saque!

218
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,083
- Cala-te.
- Espertinho.

219
00:15:03,166 --> 00:15:04,583
